data.description: Sprawling custom built ranch expanding 92ft of lot frontage situated on a private 3/4 acre lot in the golf course community of Cypress Creek.  Pride of ownership shows throughout this original owner property. The exterior lawn gas lantern invites you onto the limestone front entrance and into the tray ceiling foyer.  Brazilain cherry hardwood floors flow throughout the main living areas and into the couiffered 9ft ceiling in the dining room. Primary bedroom and 2 additional bedrooms are secluded in the right wing of the home. Left wing includes large eat in kitchen, sitting area, and great room with large stone FP.  2nd floor has 2 bonus (bedrooms) and a full bath. 3 separate floored attic spaces and tons of storage. Slate back porch and patio with peaceful water feature.  Please call for a private tour of this one of a kind property.
